    <content type="html">
      <![CDATA[<h1 id="about-me" data-svelte-h="svelte-1nwhtfo"><a href="#about-me">About me!</a></h1> <p data-svelte-h="svelte-1f6pdhf">My name is Minh Duc.</p> <p data-svelte-h="svelte-anpe9i">You can pronounce it as “Min” and “Duc” - where “Duc” sounds like “Duck”. The name “Duc” carries profound meanings in Vietnamese culture, representing virtues like morality, talent, and leadership qualities, which I strive to embody in both my personal and professional life.</p> <p data-svelte-h="svelte-ms3j0y">I am currently a third-year Information Technology student at the University of Information Technology (UIT), VNU. As I progress through my academic journey, I’m building a strong foundation in computer science fundamentals while exploring cutting-edge technologies that shape our digital future. And, I aim to become an MLOps Engineer in the future.</p> <p data-svelte-h="svelte-z16r6z">Besides, I love learning Math, code, computer, games, League of Legends, manga, swimming, gym and orca.</p> <h2 id="about-this-blog" data-svelte-h="svelte-1592ket"><a href="#about-this-blog">About this blog</a></h2> <p data-svelte-h="svelte-1a1574o">This blog simply shares my life journey.</p>]]>
    </content>
